# Foo
## Parts
* 2 nice bolts
* 1 4x2 hole plate

## Instructions
Do this and that.

# Put on the table
## Instructions
![Putting on the Table](https://d17kynu4zpq5hy.cloudfront.net/igi/opensourceecology/w5TKyEZUAnHMgxq2)

Put the table onto the bolts coming out of the working clamp supports. Those bolts will go through the 6 hole tube.

The 4 hole tube should be above the 6 hole tube.
